# Smoke Test Handoff

Before doing browser exploration for this repo:

1. Read `.cursor/smoke-test-handoff.md` to reuse the known app URL, UI flow, and prior findings.
2. Use the documented smoke-test sequence instead of rediscovering it.
3. Only gather info that is not already in the handoff note.
4. After a meaningful smoke test, update the handoff note with concise findings (what was verified, what failed, what remains unverified).
5. If you discover something new or something changed (e.g., app flow, HUD elements, test steps), update this rule and/or the handoff note so future agents have accurate guidance.
